### Payment Endpoints (Not Implemented - External Service)

### Get Payment Methods
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/payments/methods
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

###

### Get User Cards
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/payments/cards/user-123
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

###

### Save Card
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/payments/cards
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

{
  "id": "card-123",
  "user_id": "user-123",
  "payment_method_id": "pm-123",
  "pan": "4111111111111111",
  "cvv": "123",
  "expiry_month": 12,
  "expiry_year": 2025,
  "cardholder_name": "John Doe",
  "is_default": true
}

###

### Delete Card
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/v1/payments/cards/card-123
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

###

### Process Payment
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/payments/process
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

{
  "id": "txn-123",
  "order_id": "order-123",
  "user_id": "user-123",
  "payment_method_id": "pm-123",
  "amount": 25.99,
  "currency": "USD"
}

###

### Get Transaction Details
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/payments/transaction/txn-123
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

###

### Process Refund
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/payments/refund
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

{
  "transaction_id": "txn-123",
  "amount": 25.99,
  "reason": "Customer request"
}

###